{"id":363024,"type":2,"name":"风起洛阳之神机少年","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/97/e2/363024_9ZNEh.jpg","summary":"载初元年，神都洛阳。武后大权独揽，称帝在即，她向全天下发布“求才诏”，宣布重开殿试。消息一出，全国能人贤士蜂拥而至，此时洛阳城却冒出来一只肆无忌惮的狐妖，她神出鬼没，专爱偷袭年轻举子。举子接连失踪，坊间谣言漫天，百姓惶惶不安。 精通“圜诡之术”的连山堂后人裴坤也在此时来到洛阳，阴差阳错卷入了一场声势浩大的“捉妖”行动，裴坤凭一己之力击退狐妖，并揪出了潜伏在太平公主身边的春秋道杀手白鹤，高调亮相的裴坤引起洛阳城内多方势力注意。 裴坤一心想要完成师父遗愿查清当年真相，他联手羽林卫和司刑寺，并且武后的情报总管公子楚也向他抛出橄榄枝。原来公子楚早已监测到蛰伏已久的古老组织春秋道即将重现江湖，狐妖只是障眼法……","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>16</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2021年12月17日</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期五</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"中国","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":1073159,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073159","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073160,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073160","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073161,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073161","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073162,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073162","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073163,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073163","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073164,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073164","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073165,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073165","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073166,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073166","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073167,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1073167","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1073168,"url"